snippet.title: Trollhunters Defenders of Arcadia - PS4 / Xbox1 / PC / Switch
snippet.description:
Explore the Trollhunters universe as Jim Lake Jr. to stop Porgon and his sneaky plans! Team up against unknown evil forces with Claire in local co-op, upgrade your abilities and armor as you play, and even see some familiar faces along the way in this action-packed adventure!
